{"application": "software-mentions", "version": "0.8.0", "date": "2024-10-07T11:58+0000", "md5": "3CEC594FBFF3341F8557A8552E69AC9B", "mentions": [{"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 5}, "context": "mBERT, a multilingual version of BERT, is capable of learning a task in one language and of generalizing it to another. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 2.1457672119140625e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.76837158203125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 5}, "context": "mBERT, une version pr\u00e9-entra\u00een\u00e9e sur des corpus monolingues dans 104 langues, est ensuite capable d'apprendre une t\u00e2che dans une langue et de la g\u00e9n\u00e9raliser \u00e0 une autre.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.006652414798736572}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.728534698486328e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.2516975402832031e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 5}, "context": "mBERT (Fig. 1, gauche) a \u00e9t\u00e9 pr\u00e9-entra\u00een\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re non supervis\u00e9e sur deux t\u00e2ches : (1) la pr\u00e9diction de mots masqu\u00e9s al\u00e9atoirement dans un corpus multilingue et (2) une classification binaire pour d\u00e9terminer si", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.029009640216827393}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.7220458984375e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 8.463859558105469e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 10, "offsetEnd": 15}, "context": "En effet, mBERT serait capable de g\u00e9n\u00e9raliser une t\u00e2che apprise dans une langue \u00e0 une autre langue avec la d\u00e9marche sch\u00e9matis\u00e9e en Figure 1.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.012090861797332764}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.987022399902344e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.276897430419922e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 18, "offsetEnd": 23}, "context": "Des mod\u00e8les comme mBERT sont donc un bon point de d\u00e9part pour cr\u00e9er des repr\u00e9sentations multilingues coh\u00e9rentes.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.008399009704589844}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.245208740234375e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.47955322265625e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 21, "offsetEnd": 26}, "context": "\"Multilingual BERT\" (mBERT) est un mod\u00e8le de langage (Devlin et al., 2018) pr\u00e9entra\u00een\u00e9 sur un corpus de 104 langues.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022301673889160156}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.9802322387695312e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 25, "offsetEnd": 30}, "context": "Nous nous focalisons sur mBERT qui n'utilise pas de corpus parall\u00e8le et n'a pas connaissance du langage du texte en entr\u00e9e.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.015478789806365967}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.0013580322265625e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.193450927734375e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 26, "offsetEnd": 31}, "context": "Lors du pr\u00e9-entra\u00eenement, mBERT cherche \u00e0 pr\u00e9dire un mot masqu\u00e9 dans une langue donn\u00e9e.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.011169850826263428}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 9.894371032714844e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.6808509826660156e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 27, "offsetEnd": 32}, "context": "Des travaux ont montr\u00e9 que mBERT poss\u00e8de des capacit\u00e9s de g\u00e9n\u00e9ralisation multilingues suprenantes (Pires et al., 2019;Wu et Dredze, 2019), mais ne d\u00e9montrent pas que les repr\u00e9sentations des mots des diff\u00e9rentes langues qu'il construit sont align\u00e9es.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.01924312114715576}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 7.748603820800781e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.633167266845703e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 30, "offsetEnd": 35}, "context": "D'autres mod\u00e8les similaires \u00e0 mBERT existent.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.06064105033874512}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.9802322387695312e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.3113021850585938e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 43, "offsetEnd": 48}, "context": "Nous observons que l'alignement au sein de mBERT semble meilleur autour de la dixi\u00e8me couche que des premi\u00e8res ou derni\u00e8res.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.01063525676727295}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.4570693969726562e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.733966827392578e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 44, "offsetEnd": 49}, "context": "We show that the representations learned by mBERT are closer for deep layers, outperforming other representations that were specifically trained to be aligned.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 6.198883056640625e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 58, "offsetEnd": 63}, "context": "Dans nos exp\u00e9riences, les repr\u00e9sentations construites par mBERT sont compar\u00e9es avec une autre repr\u00e9sentation : des embeddings de mots FastText (Bojanowski et al., 2016) de diff\u00e9rentes langues, non-contextualis\u00e9s, align\u00e9s avec une m\u00e9thode non-supervis\u00e9e obtenant de bons r\u00e9sultats en traduction mot-\u00e0-mot (Joulin et al., 2018).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.016863763332366943}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.291534423828125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.337860107421875e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 68, "offsetEnd": 73}, "context": "Autour de cette couche profonde seulement, l'alignement produit par mBERT semble meilleur que celui de FastText align\u00e9.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.04280596971511841}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.2186508178710938e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.4080276489257812e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 69, "offsetEnd": 74}, "context": "Cependant, il semble difficile d'affirmer que les repr\u00e9sentations de mBERT sont mieux align\u00e9es.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.1044684648513794}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.337860107421875e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.800060272216797e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 74, "offsetEnd": 79}, "context": "Nous montrons que les repr\u00e9sentations de diff\u00e9rentes langues apprises par mBERT sont plus proches pour des couches profondes, et d\u00e9passent les mod\u00e8les sp\u00e9cifiquement entra\u00een\u00e9s pour \u00eatre align\u00e9s.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.013412415981292725}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.887580871582031e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 82, "offsetEnd": 87}, "context": "Nous nous int\u00e9ressons \u00e0 des embeddings multilingues contextualis\u00e9s construits par mBERT.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.002969980239868164}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.7881393432617188e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.0728836059570312e-06}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 114, "offsetEnd": 119}, "context": "Une fois les paires de mots contextualis\u00e9s extraites, il faut calculer la similarit\u00e9 de leurs repr\u00e9sentations par mBERT et la comparer avec celles de paires de mots al\u00e9atoirement extraites du corpus de traduction.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.027352631092071533}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.230571746826172e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.4437904357910156e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 155, "offsetEnd": 160}, "context": "L'intervalle de confiance \u00e0 95% des similarit\u00e9s des paires traduites chevauche peu voire pas du tout celui des paires al\u00e9atoires dans certaines couches de mBERT.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.014893174171447754}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.6226043701171875e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.5735626220703125e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 159, "offsetEnd": 164}, "context": "Il semblerait que la t\u00e2che de pr\u00e9diction de masque, cens\u00e9e \u00eatre cantonn\u00e9e \u00e0 la couche de pr\u00e9diction de masque, a en r\u00e9alit\u00e9 contamin\u00e9 les derni\u00e8res couches de mBERT.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.014012515544891357}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 6.794929504394531e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.363059997558594e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 169, "offsetEnd": 174}, "context": "Nous montrons que deux mots de langues diff\u00e9rentes, accompagn\u00e9s chacun de leur contexte, et ayant des significations proches, ont des repr\u00e9sentations proches, alors que mBERT n'a jamais \u00e9t\u00e9 sp\u00e9cifiquement entra\u00een\u00e9 pour cet alignement.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.02434098720550537}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.2159347534179688e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.270408630371094e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "mBERT", "normalizedForm": "mBERT", "offsetStart": 216, "offsetEnd": 221}, "context": "La m\u00e9thode propos\u00e9e (voir Fig. 2) consiste \u00e0 extraire, dans des phrases traduites, des paires de mots issues d'un dictionnaire bilingue et \u00e0 comparer la similarit\u00e9 des repr\u00e9sentations contextualis\u00e9es construites par mBERT pour ces paires avec des paires extraites al\u00e9atoirement.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.1882075071334839}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.6954879760742188e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.5616416931152344e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9988868832588196}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0022356510162353516}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 6.99758529663086e-05}}}], "references": [], "runtime": 8375, "id": "9fe07200b0bd42315af26c3c0925d1871461df55", "metadata": {"id": "9fe07200b0bd42315af26c3c0925d1871461df55"}, "original_file_path": "../../datalake/Samuel/SOFTware-Sync/downloads/xml/hal-03578480.grobid.tei.xml", "file_name": "hal-03578480.grobid.tei.xml"}